+- [x] Updated HomePage (App.jsx)
+- [x] Updated ToolPage.jsx
+- [x] Updated CategoryPage.jsx
+- [x] Updated AllToolsPage.jsx
+- [x] Updated AboutPage.jsx
+- [x] Updated ContactPage.jsx
