+}
+```
+
+### FAQ Schema
+```json
+{
+  "@context": "https://schema.org",
+  "@type": "FAQPage",
+  "mainEntity": [
+    {
+      "@type": "Question",
+      "name": "How accurate is this word counter?",
+      "acceptedAnswer": {
+        "@type": "Answer",
+        "text": "Our word counter is highly accurate and follows standard word counting conventions..."
+      }
+    }
+  ]
+}
+```
